Hey Builidil
<br />
I too have seen a LOT of the griping about the task system. I have not tried as yet myself. But something I have noted is that the devs specificly mentioned that the task system is NOT meant for peeps above 65. I saw that in the Q/A posted on this site.
<br />

<br />
All the bad posts I have seen have been from 66 and 67 players complaining about XP and loot. The few positive posts about the system have been from those of 40 or 50... 
<br />

<br />
I am not saying they are great since I have not done them myself but just pointing out the facts as I read them.
<br />

<br />
Also the people who like the task system are unlikely to post about it as they are generally happy. Mostly the people who are ticked off are the ones who will post so your decision MAY be based on one particular section of the community (the part that hates it).
<br />

